  "instructions": [
    "Melt the butter in the copper mug over low heat.",
    "Add the brown sugar and cook until it dissolves.",
    "Add the pitted dates and cook until they are soft and caramelized.",
    "Add the bonito flakes and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the heavy cream and vanilla extract, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook until it thickens.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve the tagine hot in the copper mug."
  ],
